TO DO WITH HIS DISCHARGE?

19:29.690 --> 19:31.387
TERMINAL UNIQUENESS.

19:31.518 --> 19:33.041
THAT'S WHY
WE LET CLAY GO.

19:33.172 --> 19:36.218
IT'S CALLED
TERMINAL UNIQUENESS.

19:36.349 --> 19:40.266
WHAT HAPPENS TO
A JUNKIE WHO THINKS
HE'S EXCEPTIONAL?

19:40.396 --> 19:44.052
