IN THEIR JOURNALS.

28:06.554 --> 28:08.208
THAT'S WHY HE WANTED
TO HIDE THEM FROM US.

28:08.338 --> 28:10.384
WELL, THAT TAKES
MOTIVE OFF THE TABLE.

28:10.514 --> 28:12.865
PRENTISS: DID WE GET
THE OTHER VICTIMS'
JOURNALS WITH A WARRANT?

28:12.995 --> 28:14.344
YEAH, WE DID.

28:14.475 --> 28:15.650
PRENTISS: WE NEED TO GO
THROUGH THEM PAGE BY PAGE.

28:17.260 --> 28:18.392
I THINK THERE'S A
VICTIMOLOGY CONNECTION
THAT WE'RE MISSING.

28:18.522 --> 28:19.915
TARA'S
ALREADY STARTED.

28:22.788 --> 28:24.441
YOU ARE NOT GONNA
BELIEVE THIS.

28:24.572 --> 28:26.922
I THINK CLAY WROTE
ABOUT THE UNSUB IN
HIS JOURNAL, AND--

28:28.881 --> 28:31.100
HI.
HI.

28:33.276 --> 28:34.408
I'M MARY. I'M, UH--

28:34.538 --> 28:37.759
HIS WIFE.
I KNOW.

28:37.890 --> 28:39.630
WHERE'S DARYL?

28:39.761 --> 28:41.415
HE'S UH...

28:41.545 --> 28:44.418
HE'S A LITTLE UPSET...

28:44.548 --> 28:49.249
AT WHAT HE COULDN'T REMEMBER
ABOUT WHAT HE DID TO YOU.

28:51.555 --> 28:53.906
CAN--UM,
CAN WE SIT?

28:54.036 --> 28:56.473
YEAH. OF COURSE.

29:02.131 --> 29:04.090
DO YOU KNOW THE 9th
OF THE 12 STEPS?

29:04.220 --> 29:05.656
I--I DO.

29:05.787 --> 29:10.009
UM...WE MADE AMENDS
TO THOSE WE HARMED.

29:10.139 --> 29:12.925
UNLESS DOING SO WOULD
INJURE THEM OR OTHERS.

29:13.055 --> 29:15.797
DARYL WANTED
TO REACH OUT TO YOU
TO MAKE AMENDS,

29:15.928 --> 29:19.714
BUT HIS SPONSOR SAID,
"LEAVE YOUR EX-WIFE ALONE.
LET HER LIVE HER LIFE.

29:19.845 --> 29:21.934
MAKE YOUR AMENDS BY
DOING BETTER NEXT TIME."

29:22.064 --> 29:24.371
IT LOOKS LIKE HE HAS.

29:26.373 --> 29:29.680
BUT...IT BOTHERED HIM,

29:29.811 --> 29:33.467
NOT SAYING A SIMPLE
"I'M SORRY"

29:33.597 --> 29:38.167
UNTIL HE STUMBLED UPON
PEOPLE WHO WERE BEING
MURDERED THAT...THAT...

29:38.298 --> 29:41.475
THAT THIS
WAS HOW HE COULD
MAKE HIS AMENDS?

29:41.605 --> 29:43.564
ONLY NOW HE FEELS
LIKE HE'S MADE IT WORSE.

29:46.001 --> 29:50.484
IF YOU COULD JUST TELL ME
HOW YOU FEEL ABOUT ALL THIS,

29:50.614 --> 29:53.182
WE COULD HELP HIM
GET PAST IT.

29:54.705 --> 29:59.493
I JUST--I SEE WHAT
HE HAS NOW,

29:59.623 --> 30:00.973
WHAT YOU HAVE
WITH HIM, AND--

30:01.103 --> 30:03.279
AND YOU'RE JEALOUS.NO.

30:05.020 --> 30:07.196
NO. I'M CONFUSED.

30:08.676 --> 30:13.507
I KILLED MYSELF
TO HELP HIM GET CLEAN.

30:13.637 --> 30:15.814
WHY COULDN'T HE GET
SOBER WITH ME?

30:15.944 --> 30:17.554
I DON'T KNOW.

30:20.383 --> 30:24.518
BUT IF IT HELPS,
I LIVE SCARED EVERY DAY.

30:24.648 --> 30:25.998
THAT HE'LL RELAPSE?

30:26.128 --> 30:29.305
NO. THAT HE'LL
LEAVE ME FOR...

30:31.786 --> 30:34.049
THE WAY HE TALKS
ABOUT YOU.

30:38.662 --> 30:40.055
HE STILL LOVES YOU.

30:42.231 --> 30:44.059
I DON'T WANT THAT.

30:45.452 --> 30:47.236
I'M HAPPY FOR HIM.

30:49.064 --> 30:52.720
I'M REALLY HAPPY
FOR YOU BOTH,

30:52.851 --> 30:57.551
BUT I DO NEED HIM.
GIVE THAT TO HIM.

30:57.681 --> 31:01.642
IT'LL TELL HIM THAT
HE WAS RIGHT ALL ALONG

31:01.772 --> 31:05.602
AND THAT I NEED
HIS HELP TO STOP
THIS KILLER.

31:07.604 --> 31:08.692
OK.

31:12.783 --> 31:14.960
PRENTISS: WE HAVE 12 INSTANCES
ON OUR END, GARCIA.

31:15.090 --> 31:16.439
HOW MANY DID YOU FIND?

31:16.570 --> 31:19.399
GARCIA: 15 SO FAR. REFERENCES
OF BROKEN WINGS, ANGELS,

31:19.529 --> 31:20.748
AND THE LIKE
ACROSS ALL JOURNALS.

31:20.879 --> 31:23.751
3 OF THE VICTIMS SAY
IT'S A METAPHOR FOR ADDICTION

31:23.882 --> 31:25.405
SUGGESTED BY
ONE OF THE STAFF.

31:25.535 --> 31:27.581
THAT STAFF MEMBER
COULD BE OUR UNSUB.

31:27.711 --> 31:30.714
BUT, GARCIA,
WE RULED OUT THE REHAB
STAFF, DIDN'T WE?

31:30.845 --> 31:32.325
YEAH. EVERYBODY
ON THE BOOKS, ANYWAY.

31:32.455 --> 31:34.718
THE UNSUB'S USE
OF MODIFIED OPIATES

31:34.849 --> 31:36.895
MAY MEAN HE'S
MEDICALLY SOPHISTICATED.

31:37.025 --> 31:41.508
IT COULD BE SOMEONE
ON THE NURSING STAFF
THAT SMITH PAYS INDIRECTLY.

31:41.638 --> 31:43.423
NOW THE QUESTION IS,
WILL SMITH HELP US?

31:43.553 --> 31:47.470
MATT, LUKE, SEE IF YOU
CAN GET THE TEMPORARY PAYROLL
INFORMATION FROM SMITH.

31:47.601 --> 31:50.604
GARCIA, START DIGGING INTO
TEMP AND TRAVELING NURSES
JUST IN CASE.

31:50.734 --> 31:52.084
AFFIRMATIVE.

31:52.214 --> 31:53.607
MAN: NICE TRY, AGENTS,

31:53.737 --> 31:55.261
BUT DR. SMITH'S
COOPERATION

31:55.391 --> 31:57.045
ONLY EXTENDS TO YOUR
MURDER INVESTIGATION.

31:57.176 --> 31:59.178
HOW HE PAYS HIS EMPLOYEES
IS OFF-LIMITS.

31:59.308 --> 32:02.703
IT'S THE SAME INVESTIGATION.
HE'S HIDING A KILLER.

32:02.833 --> 32:04.748
WE'RE DONE.

32:04.879 --> 32:06.011
HOW DO YOU THINK IT'S
GONNA AFFECT YOUR BRAND

32:07.577 --> 32:09.101
WHEN WE REVEAL
THAT YOU EMPLOYED SOMEONE
WHO THOUGHT IT WAS

32:09.231 --> 32:11.233
OK TO MURDER THE VERY
PEOPLE YOU SAY YOU'RE
TRYING TO HELP?

32:11.364 --> 32:12.626
SMITH: YOU KNOW
WHAT I THINK?

32:12.756 --> 32:15.107
I THINK I'M GOING TO
CALL A MEETING.

32:15.237 --> 32:18.284
HAVE A SIT-DOWN
WITH MOLLY, TAKE
HER INVENTORY.

32:18.414 --> 32:19.198
THAT'S A THREAT.

32:20.416 --> 32:21.635
SMITH: HOPE YOU CATCH
THIS GUY. I REALLY DO.

32:21.765 --> 32:23.942
SO TAKE IT EASY,
FELLAS.

32:24.072 --> 32:27.119
AND WHEN YOU NEED
TO GET OFF STEROIDS,
COME SEE ME.

32:32.863 --> 32:35.997
GEEZ...THEY ALL WROTE
ABOUT THEIR KILLER.

32:36.128 --> 32:39.653
YEAH, AND NOW WE HAVE
A PRETTY GOOD IDEA OF
WHO THIS GUY IS,

32:39.783 --> 32:41.481
FROM A PROFILING
PERSPECTIVE ANYWAY.

32:41.611 --> 32:43.004
HE'S AN ANGEL OF MERCY.

32:43.135 --> 32:45.659
LIKE A DOCTOR OR NURSE
WHO KILLS THEIR PATIENTS?

32:45.789 --> 32:49.271
EXACTLY. ELIZABETH
WETTLAUFER BELIEVED
GOD WANTED HER TO KILL.

32:49.402 --> 32:52.013
DONALD HARVEY KILLED
HIS PATIENTS TO
EASE THEIR PAIN.

32:52.144 --> 32:54.146
ANGELS OF MERCY HAVE
THE HIGHEST BODY COUNTS

32:54.276 --> 32:56.322
BECAUSE THEY HUNT IN
PLACES WHERE PEOPLE
TYPICALLY DIE.

32:56.452 --> 32:58.759
YEAH.

32:58.889 --> 33:02.676
FOR THIS GUY,
IT'S ALL ABOUT
THE BROKEN WING.

33:02.806 --> 33:04.765
HE GETS THEM TO
SEE THEMSELVES THIS WAY,

33:04.895 --> 33:07.550
AND IF THEY BUY IN
AND HE BELIEVES
THEY'RE TRULY BROKEN,

33:07.681 --> 33:10.162
THEY'RE NEVER GONNA
GET BETTER,

33:10.292 --> 33:11.685
I HAVE TO KILL THEM
TO END THEIR SUFFERING.

33:13.904 --> 33:15.167
FREEZE.

33:15.297 --> 33:17.691
WHAT?

33:17.821 --> 33:19.171
YOU STILL HAVE YOURS.

33:19.301 --> 33:20.563
HAVE WHAT?

33:25.742 --> 33:28.180
Y-YEAH. I, UM...

33:28.310 --> 33:29.746
YEAH.

33:34.229 --> 33:36.797
I KEEP MINE
BECAUSE IT'S A...

33:36.927 --> 33:39.539
REMINDER OF THE
WRECKAGE OF MY PAST.

33:39.669 --> 33:40.931
TARA, I...

33:41.062 --> 33:43.195
YOU KNOW,
MAYBE HE DOES, TOO.

33:43.325 --> 33:45.023
I THINK THAT'S WHAT
WE'VE BEEN MISSING HERE.

33:45.153 --> 33:46.894
I DON'T GET IT.

33:47.025 --> 33:49.244
WELL, LOOK, THIS GUY,
HE INKS HIS VICTIMS.

33:49.375 --> 33:50.767
THEY'RE HIS SIGNATURES,
HIS TROPHIES,

33:50.898 --> 33:53.553
BUT HE WOULDN'T
STOP THERE.

33:53.683 --> 33:55.250
YOU--YOU THINK HE'D
SIGN HIMSELF, TOO?

33:55.381 --> 33:56.556
LOOK AT THE DESIGN.

33:56.686 --> 33:58.210
IT'S ONE-HALF OF A
BROKEN WING. RIGHT?

33:58.340 --> 34:00.864
I'M THINKING HE PUTS
THE OTHER HALF
ON HIS BODY.

34:00.995 --> 34:03.215
AND THAT WAY, THE
WINGS ARE WHOLE AFTER
HIS VICTIMS DIE.

34:03.345 --> 34:04.738
THEY'RE COMPLETE.

34:16.271 --> 34:19.231
I THINK THIS IS
THE BEST ONE YET.

34:19.361 --> 34:20.797
CHECK IT OUT.

34:32.287 --> 34:34.246
MAN: GOOD.

34:34.376 --> 34:36.770
CLAY--HE WAS...

34:36.900 --> 34:38.293
SPECIAL.

34:42.471 --> 34:45.953
MY INSURANCE ISN'T UP.
I STILL HAVE ANOTHER
2 WEEKS.

34:46.084 --> 34:48.260
MOLLY, MOLLY, MOLLY.

34:48.390 --> 34:50.088
WHAT DID YOU THINK
WAS GONNA HAPPEN?

34:50.218 --> 34:52.568
YOU PUT YOUR NEEDS
AHEAD OF THE GROUP.

34:52.699 --> 34:54.309
WE CAN'T TOLERATE THAT.

34:54.440 --> 34:56.137
ROB, I DON'T THINK--

34:56.268 --> 34:58.096
OH, I--I THINK SO.

35:01.186 --> 35:02.622
NO.

35:02.752 --> 35:05.277
PHIL. PHIL, YOU KNOW
THIS ISN'T RIGHT.

35:05.407 --> 35:06.843
MOLLY: PHIL!

35:08.845 --> 35:10.238
IT'S UNFORTUNATE.

35:12.632 --> 35:14.286
HOW CAN THEY DO THIS?

35:14.416 --> 35:17.158
I DON'T KNOW.
I'M REALLY SORRY.

35:17.289 --> 35:19.726
I'M GONNA END UP
LIKE CLAY. I KNOW IT.

35:21.206 --> 35:24.339
IF YOU'RE THAT
WORRIED ABOUT IT,
I CAN GIVE YOU A RIDE,

35:24.470 --> 35:25.862
IF THAT'LL HELP.

35:27.212 --> 35:30.302
YEAH. YEAH.

35:30.432 --> 35:31.520
I MEAN, ARE YOU SURE?

35:31.651 --> 35:33.827
YEAH, I'M SURE.

35:33.957 --> 35:36.221
I DO THIS JOB SO
I CAN HELP PEOPLE.

35:37.787 --> 35:39.180
THANK YOU.

35:39.311 --> 35:40.877
LET ME GET THAT.

36:04.597 --> 36:06.251
GARCIA, WE GOT YOUR LIST
OF FREELANCE NURSING STAFF,

36:06.381 --> 36:08.905
BUT DID YOU CROSS-REFERENCE
CREDIT CARD RECORDS

36:09.036 --> 36:10.516
WITH LOCAL TATTOO PARLORS?

36:10.646 --> 36:11.560
YEAH, I'M DOING THAT NOW.

36:12.909 --> 36:14.433
IT LOOKS LIKE THE FREELANCERS
WERE PAID VIA SOME

36:14.563 --> 36:16.478
NATIONAL TRAVELING
NURSES ASSOCIATION.

36:16.609 --> 36:18.219
ROSSI: FOCUS ON
TEMPORARY HIRES

36:18.350 --> 36:21.657
THAT FALL IN LINE
WITH THE REHABS SMITH
VISITS DAY BY DAY.

36:21.788 --> 36:23.833
LOOK FOR OVERLAP
BETWEEN THE TWO.

36:23.964 --> 36:28.925
GARCIA: OK. I CAN SEE
THE MATRIX, PEOPLE.

36:29.056 --> 36:30.275
AH! THERE IT IS!

36:30.405 --> 36:32.886
UH, NURSE OF THE MALE
VARIETY--DOUGLAS KNIGHT.

36:33.016 --> 36:34.583
8 SESSIONS AT LOCAL
TATTOO PARLORS,

36:34.714 --> 36:35.932
ALL WITHIN HOURS
OF EACH DEATH.

36:36.063 --> 36:37.282
HERE'S HIS WORK
AND HOME ADDRESS.

36:37.412 --> 36:40.154
GREAT WORK. COPY TARA
ON WHAT YOU FOUND.

36:40.285 --> 36:43.766
WRIGHT: THIS GUY LOST
HIS WIFE DAPHNE
5 YEARS AGO TO AN OVERDOSE.

36:43.897 --> 36:45.551
THAT'S WHAT WE CALL
A STRESSOR.

36:45.681 --> 36:46.943
SO WHY DIDN'T HE START
KILLING 5 YEARS AGO?

36:47.074 --> 36:48.902
WELL, BECAUSE
THE TRIGGER CAME LATER.

36:49.032 --> 36:52.384
DOES IT SAY WHEN HE
STARTED WORKING AT ROB
SMITH'S REHAB HOUSES?

36:52.514 --> 36:54.168
YEAH, A COUPLE YEARS LATER.

36:54.299 --> 36:56.301
OK, IN AL-ANON, SINCE
I COULDN'T HELP YOU,

36:56.431 --> 36:58.607
I WAS TOLD TO LOOK
FOR THE NEXT PERSON
THAT I COULD HELP.

36:58.738 --> 37:00.130
MAYBE DOUGLAS KNIGHT
DID THE SAME.

37:00.261 --> 37:01.828
AND HE BECAME
A REHAB NURSE,

37:01.958 --> 37:03.525
AND HE WAS SURROUNDED
BY PATIENTS LIKE HIS WIFE.

37:03.656 --> 37:05.962
RIGHT. RIGHT. SO HE
HELPED AND HELPED
UNTIL HE BROKE.

37:06.093 --> 37:07.225
THAT WAS HIS TRIGGER.

37:08.791 --> 37:09.531
NOW HE THINKS HE'S
PUTTING THESE PEOPLE
OUT OF THEIR MISERY.

37:09.662 --> 37:10.837
SO WE JUST SIT HERE
AND WAIT?

37:10.967 --> 37:13.013
NO. I HAVE
A BETTER IDEA.

37:15.407 --> 37:17.322
EMILY, DID YOU
FIND HIM YET?

37:26.766 --> 37:29.029
NO, NO, NO, NO!

37:31.684 --> 37:33.468
AAH...

37:33.599 --> 37:35.470
THIS IS WHAT'S BEST.

37:35.601 --> 37:37.037
YOU'LL SEE.

37:38.343 --> 37:40.519
I'M DOING THIS
OUT OF LOVE.

37:41.737 --> 37:43.652
HEY, WHERE IS
DOUGLAS KNIGHT?

37:43.783 --> 37:46.002
IS THE FBI LOOKING
TO GET SUED OR WHAT?

37:46.133 --> 37:48.570
DOUGLAS WORKS FOR YOU.
WE NEED TO FIND HIM RIGHT NOW.

37:48.701 --> 37:50.006
PHIL:
HE ESCORTED MOLLY WITT
OUT OF THE BUILDING.

37:50.137 --> 37:51.486
PHIL, SHUT UP!
NO!

37:51.617 --> 37:53.227
THIS IS OVER.

37:53.358 --> 37:55.708
YOU WON'T HAVE TO
FEEL ANY MORE PAIN.

37:55.838 --> 37:58.537
YOU WON'T HAVE TO
HURT ANYMORE,

37:58.667 --> 38:01.757
YOU WON'T HURT
ANYONE ELSE.
PLEASE, NO!

38:01.888 --> 38:03.977
BUT I WILL ALWAYS
REMEMBER YOU.

38:06.501 --> 38:09.591
DOUGLAS KNIGHT? FBI!

38:09.722 --> 38:11.506
KNIGHT:
YOU DON'T BELONG HERE!

38:11.637 --> 38:16.032
PRENTISS:
DOUGLAS, JUST WAIT...

38:16.163 --> 38:17.512
AND LISTEN.

38:19.297 --> 38:22.517
LEWIS: DOUGLAS, I KNOW
WHAT IT'S LIKE TO LOSE
SOMEONE TO THIS DISEASE.

38:22.648 --> 38:25.172
I KNOW WHAT IT'S LIKE
TO LOSE SOMEONE
TO THIS DISEASE.

38:25.303 --> 38:28.218
ALL YOUR HOPES AND YOUR
DREAMS FOR THE FUTURE

38:28.349 --> 38:30.960
DESTROYED IN THE FACE
OF SOMETHING THAT
YOU CAN'T PREDICT.

38:31.091 --> 38:33.049
...AND YOU CAN'T CONTROL.

38:33.180 --> 38:35.095
SOMETIMES, I WANTED TO SHAKE
THE MAN I LOVED.

38:35.225 --> 38:36.923
I'D EVEN GET INTO
FISTFIGHTS WITH HIM...

38:37.053 --> 38:41.667
BECAUSE I WANTED HIM TO SEE
HOW MUCH HE'D HURT ME,

38:41.797 --> 38:45.758
UNTIL IT GOT SO BAD THAT
I HAD TO LET HIM GO.

38:45.888 --> 38:47.934
EVEN THOUGH THAT MEANT
POSSIBLY...

38:48.064 --> 38:49.805
PROBABLY LETTING HIM DIE.

38:52.808 --> 38:55.158
YOU KNOW WHAT THAT
FEELS LIKE, DON'T YOU?

38:57.422 --> 38:58.553
YES.

38:58.684 --> 39:00.163
YES, I DO.

39:00.294 --> 39:03.558
DOUGLAS,
THIS DISEASE...

39:03.689 --> 39:04.994
IT'S IMPOSSIBLE.

39:05.125 --> 39:08.737
...IMPOSSIBLE TO CURE,
IMPOSSIBLE TO PREDICT,

39:08.868 --> 39:11.827
BUT SO MANY PEOPLE
EVENTUALLY MAKE IT.

39:11.958 --> 39:15.135
ALL I CAN SAY IS,
YOU HAVE TO GIVE THEM A CHANCE.

39:17.093 --> 39:18.921
AND MOLLY DESERVES
THAT CHANCE.

39:19.052 --> 39:21.141
...BECAUSE HER DISEASE
ISN'T KILLING HER.

39:21.271 --> 39:22.751
YOU ARE.

39:22.882 --> 39:24.884
YOU NEED TO LET HER GO.

39:31.107 --> 39:32.457
LET HER GO.

39:46.732 --> 39:50.083
MOLLY! I'M GONNA GIVE YOU
A SHOT OF NALOXONE.

39:50.213 --> 39:53.173
IT'S GONNA SAVE YOUR LIFE,
BUT IT WON'T FEEL GOOD.

40:00.006 --> 40:03.531
OK, THERE YOU ARE. OK.

40:03.662 --> 40:05.141
ALL RIGHT. WE GOT YOU.

40:05.272 --> 40:08.623
MAN: ♪ WHEN YOU HOLD ME

40:08.754 --> 40:15.630
♪ YOU CAN'T EVEN SEE
THE PAIN MY FACE IS HIDING ♪

40:15.761 --> 40:22.158
♪ YOU DON'T EVEN KNOW HOW MUCH
MY HEART IS BREAKING ♪

40:22.289 --> 40:25.945
♪ BUT NOW THAT IT'S OVER

40:26.075 --> 40:29.905
♪ AND I'M SOBER

40:30.036 --> 40:35.520
♪ THE STUFF THAT I FEEL
IS SO REAL ♪

40:35.650 --> 40:42.135
♪ YOU LED ME ON,
AND I FOLLOWED YOU ♪

40:42.265 --> 40:45.355
♪ YOU'RE MY DRUG OF CHOICE

40:45.486 --> 40:49.142
♪ WHAT COULD I DO?

40:49.272 --> 40:51.753
IT'S BEAUTIFUL, ISN'T IT?

40:51.884 --> 40:54.582
♪ BUT NOW THAT IT'S OVER

40:54.713 --> 40:55.801
BEAUTIFUL.

40:55.931 --> 40:58.673
♪ AND I'M SOBER

40:58.804 --> 41:01.459
♪ THE STUFF THAT I FEEL
IS SO REAL ♪

41:01.589 --> 41:02.721
HEY.

41:04.462 --> 41:07.682
THANK YOU
FOR BELIEVING IN ME.

41:07.813 --> 41:10.642
I'VE TOLD SO MANY LIES,
I WOULDN'T HAVE TRUSTED ME.

41:12.818 --> 41:14.689
DON'T MESS IT UP
THIS TIME...

41:14.820 --> 41:16.952
WITH MARY,
ALL RIGHT?

41:17.083 --> 41:20.216
I DON'T INTEND TO.

41:20.347 --> 41:25.221
AND MARY TOLD ME
A LITTLE BIT ABOUT
WHAT YOU GUYS TALKED ABOUT,

41:25.352 --> 41:27.920
ABOUT ME NOT GETTING
SOBER FOR YOU.

41:29.748 --> 41:34.709
BUT, IN A WAY, I DID,
BECAUSE...

41:34.840 --> 41:36.668
WHEN YOU LEFT ME, THAT'S
WHEN I HIT ROCK BOTTOM.

41:36.798 --> 41:41.150
THAT'S WHEN I KNEW
I COULDN'T GO ON THAT
WAY ANYMORE, AND, UH...

41:41.281 --> 41:45.677
MY AMENDS TO YOU
IS NOT...

41:45.807 --> 41:47.766
TO SAY "I'M SORRY,"
ALTHOUGH I AM.

41:47.896 --> 41:50.290
IT'S TO TELL YOU
THAT, UH...

41:51.770 --> 41:54.903
YOU SAVED MY LIFE.

41:55.034 --> 41:57.123
AND, UH...

41:57.253 --> 41:59.255
HANDS OFF. I GET IT.

41:59.386 --> 42:01.301
BUT, UM...

42:06.785 --> 42:08.395
GET IN HERE, DUMMY.

42:12.138 --> 42:15.968
LEWIS: "THE BOND THAT LINKS YOUR
TRUE FAMILY IS NOT ONE OF BLOOD,

42:16.098 --> 42:19.754
BUT OF RESPECT AND JOY
IN EACH OTHER'S LIFE."

42:19.885 --> 42:21.321
RICHARD BACH.

